es/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時最少已經有11個香港人為咗我地被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當中包括為咗我地而食棍!!!中椒!!!同埋中槍既香港人!!!!!!<br />\n星期日上街我地一定要為佢地發聲!!!唔可以忘記佢地!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n大家集中目標:<br />\n1.撤回送中惡法<br />\n2.林鄭及相關官員必須問責下台<br />\n3.釋放所有被捕人士及保證不會檢控任何示威者<br />\n4.起訴涉嫌謀殺之警員及其上司<br />\n5.成立具效力之警方濫用暴力調查組織<br />\n6.釋放所有在囚政治人士,包括黃之鋒及梁天琦<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港人,記得一個都不能少!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n唔可以放棄任何一個自己人!!!!!!</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2558433058ab4f42329be5963b024442c673971c","tid":1220021,"uid":174367,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:27:48.000Z","msg":"推到全港中學生都響應行動！"},{"pid":"582eef5e2fbbf860c447088ac3635bdf8eb73bef","tid":1220021,"uid":13879,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"唔怪得啲家長死都要入喇沙<br />\n訓練到啲學生識思考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f42f5812e8ffe1eb6b77a0dff0d15f82350ce82d","tid":1220021,"uid":174367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:29:25.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcb3ba97db6ea7acc22b36049cae941b930de31a","tid":1220021,"uid":66957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:30:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"114f398de7ae76641b92e1112fc320d220f80a59","tid":1220021,"uid":174367,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49568d95f3f753c7c1d2384fc932c4c46d378b87","tid":1220021,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:32:09.000Z","msg":"mo la mo la, 毅進繼入U之後又可以入名校"},{"pid":"176f9c4d8d1c48b115428c83e9381cc33dd0c800","tid":1220021,"uid":217762,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T02:32:45.000Z","msg":"***轉發***<br /